        <item>
            <title>MacTR 1.3.11</title>
            <sparkle:version>1.3.11</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3.11</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <style>
                    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #333; padding: 8px; }
                    h3 { font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0 4px; }
                    ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 4px 0; }
                    li { margin: 2px 0; }
                </style>
                <h3>v1.3.11</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fix disk free/used reporting — free space now includes purgeable space (caches, snapshots, evictable cloud files) exactly as Finder reports it, instead of falsely showing a nearly-full disk</li>
                    <li>Disk capacity now uses Apple's documented volume API and reports decimal GB, matching Finder</li>
                    <li>Removed the diskutil subprocess entirely — disk stats are now a cheap native call</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0900</pubDate>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/beret21/MacTR/releases/download/v1.3.11/MacTR-1.3.11.zip"
