        <item>
            <title>MacTR 1.3.10</title>
            <sparkle:version>1.3.10</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3.10</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <style>
                    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #333; padding: 8px; }
                    h3 { font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0 4px; }
                    ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 4px 0; }
                    li { margin: 2px 0; }
                </style>
                <h3>v1.3.10</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Memory arc color now reflects real macOS memory pressure, not used% — a Mac using RAM as cache stays green instead of falsely warning</li>
                    <li>Disk capacity is now polled every ~30s instead of every 2s, keeping the diskutil subprocess off the hot path</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
