                    ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 4px 0; }
                    li { margin: 2px 0; }
                </style>
                <h3>v1.3.9</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Swap trend is now an in/out mirror chart (swap out ↑ / swap in ↓) with a center axis — visually consistent with the Network and Disk I/O charts</li>
                    <li>The center axis stays visible when idle, so a healthy no-swap state reads as "monitored" rather than broken</li>
                </ul>
