        <item>
            <title>MacTR 1.3.6</title>
            <sparkle:version>1.3.6</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3.6</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <style>
                    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #333; padding: 8px; }
                    h3 { font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0 4px; }
                    ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 4px 0; }
                    li { margin: 2px 0; }
                    .version { color: #888; font-size: 12px; }
                </style>
                <h3>v1.3.6</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fix display going blank — prevent duplicate reconnect from closing active connection</li>
                    <li>Fix race condition in metrics restart (thread-safe startMetrics)</li>
                    <li>Add os_log support — logs now visible in Console.app for debugging</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>v1.3.5</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fix metrics freeze after sleep/wake — all stats now restart reliably</li>
                    <li>Add timeout to diskutil subprocess (prevents metrics queue hang)</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 10 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0900</pubDate>
            <enclosure
